SUMMARY: DELIVERY OPTIONS: The store offers home delivery, parcel shop/locker pickup, and in-store pickup. PROVIDERS: Carriers include Česká pošta (Balíkovna), PPL, GLS, and Zásilkovna. PRICING: Home delivery costs 89 Kč. Parcel shop/locker prices range from 59 Kč to 64 Kč. In-store pickup is 15 Kč in Chrudim and 39 Kč in Prague. Free shipping is available for all methods on orders over 2,500 Kč. A packing fee of 25 Kč applies to orders under 350 Kč. NOTABLE FEATURES: Same-day in-store pickup is available in Prague and Chrudim if ordered by the morning cut-off time. Most other delivery methods offer next-day delivery for orders placed before the specified cut-off time. No information is provided for bulky item delivery, weekend delivery, or COD surcharges. WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is well-structured and easy to find on a dedicated page. It clearly outlines the costs, delivery times, and providers for each available option. The main omissions are details on COD fees and weekend services. A notable discrepancy is that the provided page belongs to Vivantis.cz, not prozdravi.cz.
